{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"39e1bd2ac7","title":"对付天津守敌的方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eb1a87a7c8","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"39e1bd2ac7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6c58705bbb","type":"paragraph","text":"对付天津守敌的方针！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"39e1bd2ac7"},{"id":"06848fd1ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月12日）林、楚：（一）路透社称，天津四代表出城谈判，回城后发表书面声明，表示尚好。（二）天津既有单独谈判，即可单独处理，可以不包括在邓宝珊的谈判之内。（三）天津之敌如能接受你们所提限时缴械之条件，你们即可不经攻击而占领天律，如该敌不能接受你们所提条件，则你们应于适当时间内攻占天津","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"39e1bd2ac7"},{"id":"f3ed646de4","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"39e1bd2ac7"},{"id":"abcb0eae09","type":"paragraph","text":"十二日二十时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给东北野战军司令员林起和华北军区司令员爱荣的电报。[2]指1949年1月9日国民党天津市参议会代表丁作部、杨云青、胡景嘉、威相九四人出城谈判，提出天津和平解决的意愿。人民解政军天津前线[3]邓宝珊，当时任国民党军华北“剩汇”总司令都副总司令，体作义","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"39e1bd2ac7"}],"page":{"id":"ff99845a7b","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"39e1bd2ac7","start":522,"end":522}}}},"__N_SSG":true}